title: HEXSYSTEM Complete Discography
description:
Includes full length albums: Black Cake, Black Cake II, Metempsychosis.
Includes EPs: Black Cake B-Sides, Ashes

Ashes, no description. Released July 24, 2015.

Pooling sedated tones with slow and relentless pulses. Metempsychosis emerges in late 2014 as the third full length album from Hexsystem. Influences include The Caretaker, Health, Moby and Akira Yamaoka. Released August 26, 2014.

Black Cake 2 is a full length electronic music album. Influences include Boards of Canada, Massive Attack, Moby, Jesper Kyd and Akira Yakaoma. Released March 18, 2013.

Black Cake B-Sides is a continually growing collection of free to use music. These tracks did not make the cut for the next official Black Cake release. Genres range from electronic, noise, industrial and post rock. Influences include Boards of Canada, Moby, Jesper Kyd and Akira Yakaoma. Released January 23, 2013.

Black Cake is a full album with influences from musicians like Boards of Canada, Jesper Kyd and Akira Yakaoma. Released April 11, 2010
